What no posts?!?!?!?!?!? Holy crap! This is one of the finest blues songs ever recorded IMO. It also really resonates with all of the proto-metal/blues of the late 60’s and 70’s. There is no way that you could have a Robert Plant or an Eric Clapton without Robert Johnson, no way. It’s just sick, he was so gifted.
